                        <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18391125-28-offence-1 t18391125-cd-27"></join>7th of November</rs>, 1 handkerchief, value 1<hi rend="italic">s</hi>., the goods of <persName id="t18391125-name-181" type="victimName">
